_sText:
I made this map to be fun. The parts of the map that are supposed to be challenging, are challenging. There is a pro room, gun room, 1337 room, jail, and balconies to camp when people fall. Enjoy!

Gun Room: basically has all the guns in it...

Pro Room: Has a camera and a button that kills everyone in the jail.

1337 Room: Has a monitor with multiple camera views. Has a button to kill everyone in the jail, buttons to capture people and teleport them into a buring cage, and a rave room with trance music and flashing lights.

Song in Rave Room: DJ Tiesto - Insomnia

REMEMBER, THIS IS THE BZ2 FILE

Have Fun!
